  <h2>Short Bio</h2>

  <p>
    Wade Minter is a technology executive, NHL Public Address Announcer, and public speaker based in Raleigh, North Carolina. He is the founder and CTO of <a href="https://suggestionox.com">Suggestion Ox</a>, the Public Address Announcer for the NHL's Carolina Hurricanes, and a longtime improv comedian and workshop facilitator. He has spoken at conferences including OSCON, RailsConf, LISA, and All Things Open on topics ranging from applied improv to hiring junior developers to building software for non-technical users.
  </p>

